title: Keynote: Responsible AI and Community [Gen Kit and IDX]
description: A welcome keynote introducing the event's theme on Responsible AI and its influence on the local developer community. Ankit and Principal Sir will set the tone for the day, outlining the agenda and vision for the future of AI in Prayagraj.

title: Session 1: Generative AI for Future Trends
description: Nishant will dive deep into AI and Generative AI and its potential impact on web development, highlighting real-world use cases and future trends in AI-powered web applications.

title: Session 2: Trust and Safety
description: Vivek will Explore the advanced mechanisms behind trust and safety at Google, keeping the web secure for billions of users every day.

title: Session 4: Serverless AI with Cloud Run GPU
description: Anubhav will cover how to deploy AI models in a serverless environment using Google Cloud Run with GPU, illustrating the benefits of scaling AI workloads with serverless technologies.

title: Lunch Break & Networking
description: Enjoy a delicious lunch and networking with fellow attendees, speakers, and organizers. An engaging opportunity for attendees to network and connect with speakers and fellow developers, fostering collaboration and sharing insights that extend beyond the event.

title: Session 5: Open source Technology
description: Unlock the vast world of knowledge with Praveen - Explore how Wikipedia and open collaboration are transforming global access to information.

title: Session 6: Utilize the Power of AI with Flutter App Development
description: Dhrumil will explore the integration of AI into Flutter applications, demonstrating how developers can make their mobile apps smarter and more intuitive with AI-powered features.

title: Photo Session
description: A group photo session for all attendees, speakers, and organizers to capture the memories of the event.

title: Closing Remarks and Networking
description: Final thoughts and appreciation for all speakers and attendees. An excellent opportunity for developers to network with industry experts and fellow attendees for future collaborations.
